HOT TUB HOTTIE chased the early pace while two wide into the turn, rallied and took command in upper stretch to inside the furlong marker then could not last in late stretch. MY GOLDEN BLING chased the early pace while inside on the turn, made a bid in mid stretch but came up empty in late stretch. LA MORENA was settled then raced four wide in upper stretch, angled inside in mid stretch and was gaining ground but was no menace. CASINO QUEEN set the early pace then drew off on the turn, was in a long drive but faltered in the stretch drive. MY BABYS GONE was unhurried early and failed to menace.
